<h2 id="设计思路" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#设计思路" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 设计思路</h2>
<p>我们按照自顶向下的原则，假设现有一个NPN管，如何在示波器上显示输出特性曲线？思考输出特性曲线的<strong>横坐标是<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>U</mi><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">U_{CE}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8333em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">U</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3283em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.109em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">CE</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，纵坐标是<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>C</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I_C</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8333em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">I</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3283em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0785em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong>，所以示波器的一个通道应该测量三极管的集电极，而电流参数<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>C</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I_C</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8333em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">I</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3283em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0785em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>可以通过<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><msub><mi>U</mi><mi>E</mi></msub><msub><mi>R</mi><mi>E</mi></msub></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\frac {U_E}{R_E}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.3339em;vertical-align:-0.4453em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8886em;"><span style="top:-2.655em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3448em;"><span style="top:-2.3567em;margin-left:-0.0077em;margin-right:0.0714em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.5em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size3 size1 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1433em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width:0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top:-3.4103em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">U</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3448em;"><span style="top:-2.3567em;margin-left:-0.109em;margin-right:0.0714em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.5em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size3 size1 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">E</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1433em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.4453em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span></span></span></span>来表征，所以可以在发射极接一个小电阻（约200Ω）、示波器探头测发射极。</p>
<p>在<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>B</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I_B</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8333em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">I</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3283em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0785em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>为定值的情况下，从<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>h</mi><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">graph1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal">a</span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span>可以看到自变量<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>U</mi><mrow><mi>C</mi><mi>E</mi></mrow></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">U_{CE}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8333em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">U</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3283em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.109em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.05764em;">CE</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>从零不断增大，所以在集电极应接入一个幅值由低到高线性变化且连续的信号——锯齿波、三角波较为复合。</p>
<p>针对输出特性曲线中含有多个（一般给出6个）不同的<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>B</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I_B</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8333em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">I</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3283em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0785em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>值，我们需要在三极管基极接入一个幅值由低到高跳变6次且不连续的信号——6阶的阶梯波正好满足需要。</p>
<p>设计具体的电路首先考虑电源的选择。考虑到电脑USB口的供电最大是5V，使用口袋仪器测量时最大供电也只能是5V，所以设计采用5V供电。</p>
<p>根据所学知识，方波积分可以产生三角波，这是容易想到的；如何产生阶梯波呢？可能会想到方波经过不同通道的分压再叠加这样一种电路来实现，但是这有一个问题，电压值相互叠加很可能超过电源电压（采用5V），<strong>如果能限定最大值是（或接近）5V就好了。</strong></p>
<p>现在可使用的器件有NE555、双运放芯片、计数器芯片和单刀八掷开关芯片，其中NE555基本上是固定用法，作为方波产生电路；运放芯片用作积分器；剩下计数器和开关，我们可以这样：<strong>5V通过6个电阻串联分压</strong>，如<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>h</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">graph2</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal">a</span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="mord">2</span></span></span></span>，得到6个电压值，然后分别送入单刀八掷开关芯片的6个输入端，通过A0、A1、A2地址选择端，控制依次输出D1~D6；计数器作分频器控，制信号由方波经过分频器产生，分频器有三个输出，从000~111依次变化（可以看到有2个节拍由于开关芯片没有输入所以输出是0）。最后开关芯片的输出就是6阶的阶梯波了。</p>
<img src="@source/课程实验/模电实验/晶体管图示仪.assets/image-20220902165856607.png" alt="image-20220902165856607" style="zoom:50%;" />
$$
graph2 \notag
$$
<h2 id="总体结构框图" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#总体结构框图" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 总体结构框图</h2>
<p><img src="@source/课程实验/模电实验/晶体管图示仪.assets/框图.png" alt="框图" loading="lazy"></p>
<Mermaid id="mermaid-382ee243" code="graph%20LR%0A%09k1(%5B%22%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%A2%E5%8F%91%E7%94%9F%E7%94%B5%E8%B7%AF%EF%BC%88%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83NE555%EF%BC%89%22%5D)%0A%09k2(%5B%22%E4%B8%89%E8%A7%92%E6%B3%A2%E5%8F%91%E7%94%9F%E7%94%B5%E8%B7%AF%EF%BC%88%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83LF353%EF%BC%89%22%5D)%0A%20%20%20%20k3(%5B%22%E9%98%B6%E6%A2%AF%E6%B3%A2%E5%8F%91%E7%94%9F%E7%94%B5%E8%B7%AF%EF%BC%88%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%8374LS169%E3%80%81CD4051%EF%BC%89%22%5D)%0A%20%20%20%20k4(%5B%22%E6%99%B6%E4%BD%93%E7%AE%A1%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E7%94%B5%E8%B7%AF%EF%BC%88%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83NPN%E4%B8%89%E6%9E%81%E7%AE%A1%E3%80%81%E7%A4%BA%E6%B3%A2%E5%99%A8%EF%BC%89%22%5D)%0A%20%20%20%20k1%20--%3E%20k2%20--%3E%20k4%0A%20%20%20%20k1%20--%3E%20k3%20--%3E%20k4%0A"></Mermaid><h2 id="分块电路和总体电路的设计" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#分块电路和总体电路的设计" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 分块电路和总体电路的设计</h2>
<h3 id="方波产生电路" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#方波产生电路" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 方波产生电路</h3>
<p>NE555的接法（用法）一般有三种：单稳态、无稳态、双稳态。产生方波需使用无稳态接法，如<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>h</mi><mn>3</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">graph3</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal">a</span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="mord">3</span></span></span></span>。</p>
<blockquote>
<p>**无稳态：**指没有稳定的状态，既不稳定于高电平，也不稳定于低电平，而是高低电平依次跳变。</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img src="@source/课程实验/模电实验/晶体管图示仪.assets/无稳态-16621764242312.png" alt="无稳态" loading="lazy"></p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>h</mi><mn>3</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
graph3 \notag
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal">a</span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="mord">3</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>考虑到后级电路会接运放，需确定频率。</p>
<p><strong>控制输出频率：</strong></p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mi>l</mi><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn><mo separator="true">⋅</mo><mi>C</mi><mo separator="true">⋅</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>R</mi><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>R</mi><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
f=\frac {1}{ln2·C·(R1+2R2)}
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:2.2574em;vertical-align:-0.936em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.3214em;"><span style="top:-2.314em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.01968em;">l</span><span class="mord mathnormal">n</span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mpunct">⋅</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span><span class="mpunct">⋅</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">+</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span><span style="top:-3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width:0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top:-3.677em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.936em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>查阅LF353的手册，可知其压摆率典型值为13V/us，供电±5V时最大输出幅度与频率的关系如<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>h</mi><mn>4</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">graph4</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal">a</span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="mord">4</span></span></span></span>。</p>
<p><img src="@source/课程实验/模电实验/晶体管图示仪.assets/image-20220903121507039.png" alt="image-20220903121507039" loading="lazy"></p>
<p><img src="@source/课程实验/模电实验/晶体管图示仪.assets/image-20220903121700673.png" alt="image-20220903121700673" loading="lazy"></p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>h</mi><mn>4</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
graph4 \notag
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal">a</span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="mord">4</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>对一个正弦波来说，其最大变化速率发生在过零点处，且与输出信号幅度、频率有关。</p>
<p>设输出正弦波幅度为<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>A</mi><mi>m</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">A_m</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8333em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">A</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1514em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">m</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，频率为<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>f</mi><mrow><mi>o</mi><mi>u</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f_{out}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2806em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.1076em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">o</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">u</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">t</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，过零点变化速率为<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>D</mi><mi>V</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">D_V</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8333em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3283em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.22222em;">V</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，则</p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>𝐷</mi><mi>𝑉</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>π</mi><msub><mi>𝐴</mi><mi>𝑚</mi></msub><msub><mi>𝑓</mi><mrow><mi>o</mi><mi>u</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
𝐷_𝑉=2π𝐴_𝑚𝑓_{out}
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8333em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3283em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.22222em;">V</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">π</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">A</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1514em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">m</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2806em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.1076em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">o</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">u</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">t</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>要想输出完美的正弦波，则正弦波过零点变化速率必须小于运放的压摆率。即</p>
<p class='katex-block katex-error' title='Error: Font metrics not found for font: .'>
SR&gt;𝐷_𝑉=2𝜋𝐴_𝑚𝑓_{out}
</p>
<p>假设工作频率为10kHz，则据<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>h</mi><mn>4</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">graph4</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal">a</span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="mord">4</span></span></span></span>可知输出峰值约4.5V，<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>D</mi><mi>V</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>∗</mo><mi>π</mi><mo>∗</mo><mn>4.5</mn><mo>∗</mo><mn>10</mn><mi>k</mi><mo>≈</mo><mn>282.6</mn><mi>k</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">D_V=2*π*4.5*10k≈282.6k</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8333em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3283em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.22222em;">V</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6444em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">∗</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.4653em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">π</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">∗</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6444em;"></span><span class="mord">4.5</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">∗</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6944em;"></span><span class="mord">10</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03148em;">k</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">≈</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6944em;"></span><span class="mord">282.6</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03148em;">k</span></span></span></span>，又SR=1300kV/s（注意单位），显然<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>S</mi><mi>R</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mo>&gt;</mo><msub><mi>D</mi><mi>V</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">SR&gt;&gt;D_V</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.7224em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">SR</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">&gt;&gt;</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8333em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3283em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.22222em;">V</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，且可以看到50k以下的频率都不会越过压摆率的限制。由此可以确定（1）式中的参数。可选择C=1200pF、R1=1k、R2=50k，理论算出频率约8.33kHz。</p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>备注</strong></p>
<p>实物搭设电路时，对这几个参数作微小的变动是可能的。</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="三角波产生电路" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#三角波产生电路" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 三角波产生电路</h3>
<p>三角波由方波积分产生。基本积分电路：</p>
<p><img src="@source/课程实验/模电实验/晶体管图示仪.assets/image-20220903132911860.png" alt="image-20220903132911860" loading="lazy"></p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>v</mi><mi>o</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mi>R</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow></mfrac><msubsup><mo>∫</mo><mn>0</mn><mi>t</mi></msubsup><mrow><msub><mi>v</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mi>d</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>v</mi><mi>o</mi></msub><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>t</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
v_o=-\frac{1}{RC} \int_0^t {v_1(t)dt} + v_o(t)
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.5806em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">v</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1514em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0359em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">o</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:2.4554em;vertical-align:-0.9119em;"></span><span class="mord">−</span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.3214em;"><span style="top:-2.314em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">RC</span></span></span><span style="top:-3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width:0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top:-3.677em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.686em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mop"><span class="mop op-symbol large-op" style="margin-right:0.44445em;position:relative;top:-0.0011em;">∫</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.5435em;"><span style="top:-1.7881em;margin-left:-0.4445em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">0</span></span></span><span style="top:-3.8129em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">t</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.9119em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">v</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3011em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0359em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">t</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mord mathnormal">d</span><span class="mord mathnormal">t</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">+</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">v</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1514em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0359em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">o</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal">t</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>备注</strong></p>
<p>实际电路应在电容上并联一电阻，一般取10k左右即可。</p>
<p>实际的积分器由于运算放大器难免会存在偏置电压，尽管偏置电压很低，还是会对电容进行充放电，时间一长，电容就饱和了。并联电阻的目的就是为了使给电容提供放电回路，不要饱和。</p>
</blockquote>
<p>根据前文所述，晶体管集电极需接入<strong>正</strong>的三角波，而方波经过该积分电路是<strong>负的</strong>，所以需再经过一级反相放大。</p>
<p>基本反相放大器：</p>
<p><img src="@source/课程实验/模电实验/晶体管图示仪.assets/image-20220903133803291.png" alt="image-20220903133803291" loading="lazy"></p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>v</mi><mi>o</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac><msub><mi>R</mi><mi>F</mi></msub><msub><mi>R</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><msub><mi>v</mi><mi>I</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
v_o=-\frac {R_F}{R_1}v_I
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.5806em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">v</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1514em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0359em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">o</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:2.1963em;vertical-align:-0.836em;"></span><span class="mord">−</span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.3603em;"><span style="top:-2.314em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3011em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0077em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width:0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top:-3.677em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3283em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0077em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">F</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.836em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">v</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3283em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0359em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">I</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>还可以根据积分器的输出适当引入偏置，使反相放大器的输出从零开始增加，即从+VCC引出一条导线，串联合适的电阻<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>R</mi><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">R0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span>，再接入反向输入端。</p>
<p>调节放大倍数使输出幅值接近4.5V（参考<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>h</mi><mn>4</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">graph4</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal">a</span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="mord">4</span></span></span></span>）。<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>R</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">R_1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8333em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3011em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0077em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>取10k，在仿真中反复调节<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>R</mi><mn>0</mn><mtext>、</mtext><msub><mi>R</mi><mi>F</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">R0、R_F</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8333em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">、</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3283em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0077em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">F</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，最终<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>R</mi><mi>F</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">R_F</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8333em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3283em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0077em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">F</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>取100k、<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>R</mi><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">R0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span>取21k较为合适。电路如<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>h</mi><mn>5</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">graph5</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal">a</span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="mord">5</span></span></span></span>。</p>
<p><img src="@source/课程实验/模电实验/晶体管图示仪.assets/image-20220903172252108.png" alt="image-20220903172252108" loading="lazy"></p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>h</mi><mn>5</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
graph5 \notag
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal">a</span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="mord">5</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<h3 id="阶梯波产生电路" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#阶梯波产生电路" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 阶梯波产生电路</h3>
<p>对于阶梯波发生器的设计思路，前文已有阐述，此处不再赘述。需要注意的是仿真中没有CD4051的模型，可用ADG408代替，实物连接时应根据CD4051的数据手册中给出的封装引脚图。电路如<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>h</mi><mn>6</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">graph6</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal">a</span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="mord">6</span></span></span></span>。</p>
<p><img src="@source/课程实验/模电实验/晶体管图示仪.assets/image-20220903173830369.png" alt="image-20220903173830369" loading="lazy"></p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>h</mi><mn>6</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
graph6 \notag
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal">a</span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="mord">6</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<h3 id="晶体管测试电路" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#晶体管测试电路" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 晶体管测试电路</h3>
<p>据前文所述，三角波接入集电极，阶梯波接入基极。电路如<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>h</mi><mn>7</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">graph7</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal">a</span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="mord">7</span></span></span></span>。</p>
<p><img src="@source/课程实验/模电实验/晶体管图示仪.assets/image-20220903174853523.png" alt="image-20220903174853523" loading="lazy"></p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>h</mi><mn>7</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
graph7 \notag
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal">a</span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="mord">7</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>可以看到基极串联了一个较大的电阻（100kΩ），这是因为<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>I</mi><mi>B</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">I_B</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8333em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07847em;">I</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3283em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0785em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">B</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>都是几十μA级的，而阶梯波的幅度为0~4.5V，需接入较大的电阻。</p>
<p>然后集电极接示波器A通道，发射极接B通道，示波器设置为B/A即可。</p>
<h3 id="总体电路" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#总体电路" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 总体电路</h3>
<p>针对该系统，前后级电路直接耦合即可。</p>
<p>另外，在各芯片电源引脚与地之间并联两个电容（一般0.1μF/10μF），即旁路电容，对电源去耦，使高频噪声接地，可一定程度上提高系统的稳定性。</p>
<p><img src="@source/课程实验/模电实验/晶体管图示仪.assets/image-20220903175502184.png" alt="image-20220903175502184" loading="lazy"></p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>h</mi><mn>8</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
graph8 \notag
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal">a</span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="mord">8</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<h3 id="所实现功能说明" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#所实现功能说明" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 所实现功能说明</h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>设计一个阶梯波发生器，<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo>≥</mo><mn>500</mn><mi>H</mi><mi>z</mi><mtext>，</mtext><msub><mi>U</mi><mrow><mi>o</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow></msub><mo>≥</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>V</mi><mtext>，阶数</mtext><mi>N</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f≥500Hz，U_{opp}≥3V，阶数N=6</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">≥</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.9694em;vertical-align:-0.2861em;"></span><span class="mord">500</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.04398em;">Hz</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">，</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">U</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1514em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.109em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">o</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">pp</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2861em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">≥</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord">3</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.22222em;">V</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">，阶数</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">N</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6444em;"></span><span class="mord">6</span></span></span></span></strong></p>
<p>测试时先测量74LS169的三个输出端口，即<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>h</mi><mn>8</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">graph8</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal">a</span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="mord">8</span></span></span></span>中的<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>Q</mi><mi>A</mi><mtext>、</mtext><mi>Q</mi><mi>B</mi><mtext>、</mtext><mi>Q</mi><mi>C</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">QA、QB、QC</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8778em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">Q</span><span class="mord mathnormal">A</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">、</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.05017em;">QB</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">、</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">QC</span></span></span></span>端口，看是否为三种频率的方波，且相互为二倍频；否则说明电路有误。</p>
<p>若上述过程无误，测试过程中发现阶数小于6，可能是<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>h</mi><mn>8</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">graph8</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal">a</span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="mord">8</span></span></span></span>中的<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>R</mi><mn>7</mn><mtext>、</mtext><mi>R</mi><mn>11</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>R</mi><mn>15</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">R7、R11 - R15</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.7667em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="mord">7</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">、</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="mord">11</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="mord">15</span></span></span></span>中某个或多个被短路，注意检查这六个电阻有无短路。</p>
<p>若发现阶梯波下降沿较慢，可适当降低工作频率，即增大<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>h</mi><mn>8</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">graph8</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal">a</span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="mord">8</span></span></span></span>中的<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>R</mi><mn>1</mn><mtext>、</mtext><mi>R</mi><mn>2</mn><mtext>或</mtext><mi>C</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">R1、R2或C2</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">、</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">或</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span><span class="mord">2</span></span></span></span>。</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>使用口袋仪器测量：</p>
<p><img src="@source/课程实验/模电实验/晶体管图示仪.assets/image-20220903184541902.png" alt="image-20220903184541902" loading="lazy"></p>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>591.3</mn><mi>H</mi><mi>z</mi><mtext>，</mtext><msub><mi>U</mi><mrow><mi>o</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>4.3</mn><mi>V</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mtext>阶数</mtext><mi>N</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">f=591.3Hz，U_{opp}=4.3V,阶数N=6</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.9694em;vertical-align:-0.2861em;"></span><span class="mord">591.3</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.04398em;">Hz</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">，</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">U</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1514em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.109em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">o</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">pp</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2861em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8778em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord">4.3</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.22222em;">V</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">阶数</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">N</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6444em;"></span><span class="mord">6</span></span></span></span>，满足要求</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>使用实验室仪器测量：</p>
<p><img src="@source/课程实验/模电实验/晶体管图示仪.assets/image-20220903184844968.png" alt="image-20220903184844968" loading="lazy"></p>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>T</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4.2</mn><mo>∗</mo><mn>400</mn><mi>μ</mi><mi>s</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1680</mn><mi>μ</mi><mi>s</mi><mtext>，</mtext><mi>f</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>595.2</mn><mi>H</mi><mi>z</mi><mtext>，</mtext><msub><mi>U</mi><mrow><mi>o</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>4.2</mn><mi>V</mi><mtext>，阶数</mtext><mi>N</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">T=4.2*400μs=1680μs，f=595.2Hz，U_{opp}=4.2V，阶数N=6</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.13889em;">T</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6444em;"></span><span class="mord">4.2</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">∗</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8389em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord">400</span><span class="mord mathnormal">μ</span><span class="mord mathnormal">s</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord">1680</span><span class="mord mathnormal">μ</span><span class="mord mathnormal">s</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">，</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.9694em;vertical-align:-0.2861em;"></span><span class="mord">595.2</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.04398em;">Hz</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">，</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">U</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1514em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.109em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">o</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">pp</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2861em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord">4.2</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.22222em;">V</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">，阶数</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">N</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6444em;"></span><span class="mord">6</span></span></span></span>，满足要求。</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>设计一个三角波发生器，三角波<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>U</mi><mrow><mi>o</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow></msub><mo>≥</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>V</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">U_{opp}≥2V</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.9694em;vertical-align:-0.2861em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">U</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1514em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.109em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">o</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">pp</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2861em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">≥</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.22222em;">V</span></span></span></span></strong></p>
<p>先测试第一片运放的输出端口，即<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>h</mi><mn>8</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">graph8</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">g</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">r</span><span class="mord mathnormal">a</span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mord mathnormal">h</span><span class="mord">8</span></span></span></span>中的U4A的1脚，看是否有基本的三角波形状；否则，主要调节<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>C</mi><mn>3</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">C3</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.07153em;">C</span><span class="mord">3</span></span></span></span>。</p>
<p>若上述过程无误，测量U3B的7脚，看是否为包含0V、峰峰值超过2V的三角波。若峰峰值太小，则增大<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>R</mi><mn>8</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">R8</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="mord">8</span></span></span></span>，增加放大倍数，且根据实验观察这时一般伴随着偏置电压的调节，即调节<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>R</mi><mn>9</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">R9</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="mord">9</span></span></span></span>。</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>使用口袋仪器测量：</p>
<p><img src="@source/课程实验/模电实验/晶体管图示仪.assets/image-20220903195318300.png" alt="image-20220903195318300" loading="lazy"></p>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>U</mi><mrow><mi>o</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mi>V</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">U_{opp}=4V</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.9694em;vertical-align:-0.2861em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">U</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1514em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.109em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">o</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">pp</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2861em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord">4</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.22222em;">V</span></span></span></span>，满足要求。</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>使用实验室仪器测量：</p>
<p><img src="@source/课程实验/模电实验/晶体管图示仪.assets/image-20220903195725455.png" alt="image-20220903195725455" loading="lazy"></p>
<p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>U</mi><mrow><mi>o</mi><mi>p</mi><mi>p</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>3.8</mn><mi>V</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">U_{opp}=3.8V</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.9694em;vertical-align:-0.2861em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">U</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1514em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.109em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">o</span><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">pp</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2861em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord">3.8</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.22222em;">V</span></span></span></span>，满足要求。</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>设计保护电路，实现对三极管输出特性的测试</strong></p>
<p>可在放大器的输出引脚通过±5V的稳压管接地，以保护芯片。</p>
<p>连接好示波器后，可适当调节<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>R</mi><mn>17</mn><mtext>、</mtext><mi>R</mi><mn>18</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">R17、R18</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="mord">17</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">、</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.00773em;">R</span><span class="mord">18</span></span></span></span>，使输出特性曲线更加美观。</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>使用口袋仪器测量：</p>
<p><img src="@source/课程实验/模电实验/晶体管图示仪.assets/image-20220903202253252.png" alt="image-20220903202253252" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>使用实验室仪器测量：</p>
<p><img src="@source/课程实验/模电实验/晶体管图示仪.assets/image-20220903202410180.png" alt="image-20220903202410180" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
